data.description: Spacious, open concept 2 story in a gated community. This home was built as a semi custom with lots of extras. Coming in the front door the foyer welcomes you with 5" hardwoods that span the entire main floor. To the left there's a living room or office space. To the right a large dining room that could house at least all the immediate family. The cousins can sit in the breakfast area that's situated between the kitchen and family room! The master is on the main which means no more climbing stairs after falling asleep on the couch! The master suite includes a spa like bathroom with double, frameless shower as well as granite tops on the vanity and a HUGE master closet. The kitchen is open to the family room as well as the keeping room where you'll find a brick fireplace in both rooms. Yes, you could have 2 fires burning and see them both from the kitchen! Quartz countertops, a farm sink and stainless appliances along with white cabinets is the theme of this beautiful space. Coming from the garage you'll find a built in coat rack and mud room area and the laundry room is on the left. The walk in pantry is just past the mud room. The family room includes built ins and coffered ceiling with lots of light from huge windows on the back side. The back covered patio is perfect for game days with a built in fireplace and a spot for a huge screen TV. Upstairs there are 3 spacious bedrooms, all ensuite and a media room large enough to hold the entire soccer team. If you need space for the Ferrari or the golf cart there's a separate carriage garage. Located within 5 minutes of I85 and Chateau Elan or 7 min to Hamilton Mill.
